title: #USBMgmtService.v1_0_0.USBMgmtService

^([a-zA-Z_][a-zA-Z0-9_]*)?@(odata|Redfis.description: This property shall specify a valid odata or Redfish property.

ServiceEnabled.description: This property indicates whether the USB mgmt service is enabled.
ServiceEnabled.longDescription: The value is of a Boolean type which indicates whether the USB mgmt service is enabled.

USBDevicePresence.description: This property indicates whether the USB Device is present.
USBDevicePresence.longDescription: The value is of a Boolean type which indicates whether the USB Device is present.

USBUncompressPassword.description: This property indicates the USB uncompress password.
USBUncompressPassword.longDescription: The value is of a string type which indicates the USB uncompress password.

USBMgmtService.description: This is the USB mgmt service information.
USBMgmtService.longDescription: USB mgmt service information, including the enablement status and domain controller information.
